               <msContents>
                  <summary>Prayer of Moses, Wisest of the Wise, Image of Saint George, መልክአ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡, Prayer of the Covenant, ጸሎተ፡ ኪዳን፡, Mystagogia, ትምህርተ፡ ኅቡዓት፡, Anaphora of Our Lord, ቅዳሴ፡ እግዚእ፡, Anaphora of Mary attributed to Cyriacus, ቅዳሴ፡ ማርያም፡, Image of Raguel, መልክአ፡ ራጉኤል፡ and other Prayers</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="1r" to="37r" facs="003">Fols 1r–37r</locus><title>Prayer of Moses which Saved Him from Pharoah, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ጸሎተ፡ ሙሴ፡</foreign></title><incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/>ንነግረክሙ፡ ንሕነ፡ በዘድኅነ፡ ሙሴ፡ እምእዴሁ፡ ለፈርዖን። ጸሎቱ፡ ወስእለቱ፡ ለሙሴ፡ ዘወሀቦ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ መግረሬ፡ ፀር፡ ወቀዲሙሰ፡ ወረደ፡ ገብርኤል፡ መልአክ [፡] ወይቤሎ [፡] ኢትፍራህ፡ ሙሴ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  <note>excluding <locus target="#25r #25v #26r #26v" facs="027 028 028 029">fols. 25r, 25v, 26r, 26v</locus></note>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2"><locus from="25r" to="26v" facs="027">(beginning folios)</locus><locus from="75r" to="84v" facs="077"> (84v–75r; the quire is upside down)</locus><locus from="53r" to="53v" facs="055"> (concluding folios)</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2393tabiba">Ṭabiba
                                                  ṭabibān</title>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                  ኦእግዚአብሔር፡ ጠቢበ፡ ጠቢባን፡ ከሀሊ፡
                  እስከ፡ ለዓለም፡ እምጥንት፡ እንተ፡ ኢትበሊ።
                  ድኩመ፡ ሕሊና፡ ገብርከ፡ ወፈራሄ፡ ልብ፡ ኢተሀባሊ፡
                  እስመ፡ ኀቤከ፡ እግዚኦ፡ ጸሎተ፡ አድኅኖ፡ እጼሊ።
                  አድኅነኒ፡ አድኅነኒ፡ እምኵሉ፡ ቀታሊ።
                </incipit>
                 <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                 <note>This work is complete, but the folios have been rebound in disorder</note>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3"><locus from="38r" to="46r" facs="040">Fols 38r–46r</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2866RepCh147">Malkǝʾ-hymn to St
                                                  George</title><incipit xml:lang="gez">ሰላም፡ ለዝክረ፡ ስምከ፡ ዘሰሌዳ፡ ሞገስ፡ መጽሐፉ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
                <msItem xml:id="ms_i4"><locus from="46r" to="48r" facs="048">Fols 46r–48r</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3100RepCh380">Malkǝʾa
                                                  Giyorgis</title><incipit xml:lang="gez">ኦ፡ ፍጡነ፡ ረድኤት፡ ለጽኑዕ፡ ወለድኩም።
                ወለነፍሰ፡ ኵሉ፡ ቃውም።
                ጊዮርጊስ፡ የዋህ፡ እንበለ፡ መሥፈርት፡ ወአቅም።
                ከመ፡ እግዝእትከ፡ ቡርክት፡ ማርያም።
                ርኅሩኀ፡ ልብ፡ አንተ፡ እምበቀል፡ ወቂም።</incipit>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
                <msItem xml:id="ms_i5"><locus from="48v" to="49v" facs="051">Fols 48v–49v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4006Taamme">Taʾammǝra
