                <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                <note>One Miracle of Saint George, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ተአምረ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡</foreign>, How the son of Persian Governor Niqeyorǝyos had leprosy; How the governor vowed to give gold to the church of Saint George if he were healed; How the son was healed when they arrived at the church.</note>
