                    <locus target="#1r #25r #38r #54r #85r #99r" facs="003 027 040 056 087 101">1r, 25r, 38r, 54r, 85r, 99r, </locus> (colorful harägs);
                    <locus target="#6r #9v #14r #19v #24v #46r #79r #84r #97v" facs="008 012 016 022 027 048 081 086 100">6r, 9v, 14r, 19v, 24v, 46r, 79r, 84r, 97v, </locus> (line of alternating red and black dots);
                    <locus target="#32v #35v #49v #59r #68v #69r #69v #73r #97r #97v #106r" facs="035 038 052 061 071 072 075 099 100 108">32v, 35v, 49v, 59r, 68v, 69r, 69v, 73r, 97r, 97v, 106r</locus> (multiple full stops)
                    </decoNote>
                  </decoDesc>
                  <additions>
                  <list>
                    <item xml:id="a1">
                    <locus target="#iv(erso)" facs="003">Fol. iv(erso)</locus>
                    <desc type="GuestText">
                    except for last four lines: Concluding prayer (in the form of an rhyming image), typically used for a homily for the archangel or a synaxarium entry, etc.
                    Incipit: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዘእቅረብኩ፡ ማኅሌተ፡ አዘኪርየ፡ አእላፈ።
                    እምዕለ፡ ተጸምዱከ፡ ዘልፈ።
                    ለለይትነበብ፡ ተወከፍ፡ ዘንዴትየ፡ መጽሐፈ።
                    እንተ፡ ረሰይከ፡ እግዚኦ፡ ጸሪቀ፡ መበለት፡ ውኩፈ።
                    እምለ፡ ዐብዑ፡ ብዑላን፡ ዘተርፈ። <gap reason="omitted"/></foreign>
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="a2">
                    <locus target="#52r" facs="054">Fol. 52r</locus>
                    <desc type="Asmat">
                    Asmat prayer against fire and lightning.
                    Text: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ቅብርናኤም፡ ፍልፍልናየም፡ ጽብርናኤም። አድኅነኒ፡ እምነበልባል፡ ወእም፡ አየራዊ፡ መብረቅ። ሊተ፡ ለገብርከ፡ እገሌ። ። ፯።</foreign>
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="a3">
                    <locus target="#73v" facs="076">Fol. 73v</locus>
                    <desc type="Asmat">
                    in light ink: Asmat prayer against chest pain, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ሕማመ፡ ውግዓት፡.</foreign>
                    Incipit: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሰላም፡ ለገቦከ፡ ኵናተ፡ ለንጊኖስ፡ ዘወግኦ። ሳዶር፡
                    ወለነቅአ ማይ፡ ከርስከ፡ ለመስርአት፡ እንተ ኣንቅኦ፤ አላዶር፡
                    ቃለ[፡]አብ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ዘፈጸምከ፡ ግብረ፡ ተሰብኦ። ዳናት፡
                    እቀበኒ፡ በመስቀልከ፡ ለመልአከ፡ አለም፡ ዘሞኦ። አዴራ፡
                    ከመ[፡] ኖላዊ፡ የአቅብ፡ እምተ፡ ኩላ፡ በግኦ። ሮዳስ፤ <gap reason="omitted"/></foreign>
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="a4">
                    <locus target="#97v #98r" facs="100">Fols. 97v, 98r</locus>
                    <desc type="GuestText">
                    <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2999RepCh279">Hymn to John the
                                                  Baptist</title> in a later hand
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="a5">
                    <locus target="#108r" facs="110">Fol. 108r</locus>
                    <desc type="GuestText">
                    Excerpt of <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2934RepCh215">Malkǝʾ-hymn to
                                                  Raphael</title>, written in pencil, incomplete at the end
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e1">
                    <locus target="#ir(ecto) #iiv(erso) #37v #50r #52v #74r #108v" facs="001 003 040 052 055 076 111">Fols. ir(ecto), iiv(erso), 37v, 50r, 52v, 74r, 108v</locus>
                    <desc>
                    (except for heart in circle): blank
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="a7">
                    <locus target="#iv(erso)" facs="002"> f. iv(erso), last four lines</locus>
                    <desc type="CalendaricNote">
                    List of the Feast days of the Saints, George and <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS9162TaklaHa">Takla Hāymānot</persName> and <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS4306GabraMa">Gabra Manfas Qǝddus</persName>
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="a8">
                    <locus target="#iir(ecto)" facs="002"> f. iir(ecto), top</locus>
                    <desc type="CalendaricNote">
                    List of the Feast days of the Apostles
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="a9">
                    <locus target="#iir(ecto)" facs="002"> f. iir(ecto), bottom</locus>
                    <desc>
                    a calculation of the number of years from the creation of the world up to 1917 E.C., and a note on the date of the death of Empress Zäwditu (1917–30)
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="a10">
                    <locus target="#52r" facs="054">Fol. 52r</locus>
                    <desc>
                    Note: “The number of [features of] the image of Saint George with its conclusion is 51.”
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="a11">
                    <locus target="#66v #85v #86r" facs="069 088">Fols. 66v, 85v, 86r</locus>
                    <desc>
                    mentions Abba Peṭros (presumably, Peṭros VII Patriarch of Alexandria, 1810–1852), and Abba Qerǝlos (presumably Metropolitan Qerǝlos II, 1815–1828)
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e2">
                    <locus target="#102v" facs="105"> f. 102v, col. 1</locus>
                    <desc>
                    note in a later hand, written over erased text: “This book was written in the year 5,516 of the creation of the world, during the reign of Tewodros.”
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e3">
                    <locus target="#66" facs="068">Fol. 66</locus>
                    <desc>
                    brown thread is sewn into the top edge to mark content as navigation system
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e4">
                    <locus target="#33r #33v #34r #55r #59v #60r" facs="035 036 036 057 062 062">Fols. 33r, 33v, 34r, 55r, 59v, 60r</locus>
                    <desc>
                    (etc.) words of text are written interlinearly;
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e5">
                    <locus target="#38v #53r" facs="041 055">Fols. 38v, 53r</locus>
                    <desc>
                    lines of text are written interlinearly;
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e6">
                    <locus target="#36r" facs="038"> f. 36r, col. 1, line 3</locus>
                    <desc>
                    lines of text are written interlinearly with a symbol (┴) marking the location where the text is to be inserted;
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e7">
                    <locus target="#57v" facs="060">Fol. 57v</locus>
                    <desc>
                    erasure markings are visible'
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e8">
                    <locus target="#9r #25v #55r #57v #59r" facs="011 028 057 060 061">Fols. 9r, 25v, 55r, 57v, 59r</locus>
                    <desc>
                    (etc.) text has been removed
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                  </list>
                </additions>
                <bindingDesc>
                  <binding xml:id="binding" contemporary="true">
                    <decoNote xml:id="b1">Parchment, four Coptic chain stitches attached with bridle attachments to wooden boards wrapped in tooled leather, leather cover wraps around spine.</decoNote>
                    <decoNote xml:id="b2" type="bindingMaterial">
                      <material key="parchment"/>
                      <material key="wood"/>
                      <material key="leather"/>
                    </decoNote>
                  </binding>
                </bindingDesc>
               </physDesc>
               <history>
                  <origin>
                     <origDate notBefore="1815" notAfter="1828">1815-1828 (<locus target="#66v #85v #86r" facs="069 088">fols. 66v, 85v, 86r</locus>, Peṭros, Patriarch of Alexandria [1810–1852], Metropolitan Qerǝlos II [1815–1828]).</origDate>
                  </origin>
               </history>
            </msDesc>
         </sourceDesc>
